  "body": "**FastPlayBungee** is a simple plugin designed to implement commands **/<server-name>** and **/play <server-name>** for users across your network!\n\nTo join a server you require:\n- permission to **join** the server (if **restricted access** is enabled);\n- permission \"*fastplaybungee.<server-name>*\"\n- the server to be online!\n\nAlso, the command /play requires the permission \"*fastplaybungee.play*\".",
